Offbeat experience in vietnam 🇻🇳🫶🏻
( Share with someone ) ↗️

CAO BANG LOOP 🔁 🛵

From breathtaking mountain views to serene rivers and stunning waterfalls… this loop is a must-do for adventure lovers 🤪

I did 3 days 2 nights tour with an easy rider 🛵

Day 1: 55km 
• Visiting Lenin Stream, Pac Bo cave, Ho Chi Minh Memorial, Milestone KM 0 on Ho Chi Minh Road

Day 2: 120km
• Visiting Angel Mountain
• Visiting Ngao Cave (Tiger Cave), Truc Lam pagoda
• Visiting Bản Giốc Waterfall, This is the 4th largest waterfall in the world located on the border.

Day 3: 90km
• Visiting Paper village, Phja Thap Incense village, Pac Rang forging village

If you’re looking for an offbeat adventure away from the crowds, this is the perfect adventure ! 🛵🫶🏻

Thanks @getyourguidecommunity @getyourguide 🥰
